18,IssuesEvent,2015-03-21 12:48:17+00:00,3462960,lazka/pgi,438648,pwaller,,,closed,Bug in code generation: PopplerRectangle** [out] arg mistreated,"[{'url': 'https://api.github.com/repos/lazka/pgi/labels/bug', 'name': 'bug', 'color': 'e11d21'}]",[],6,"Code to reproduce:

(assumes you have `gir1.2-poppler-0.18` available.)

```python
from pgi.repository import Poppler as P

