467,IssuesEvent,2017-11-27 12:52:24+00:00,6662075,joke2k/faker,664779,maxnordlund,,,opened,Option for emitting safe phone numbers only,[],[],0,"Hi, thanks for this lovely library. The current phone number generator emits invalid ones, as pointed out by [python-phonenumbers](https://github.com/daviddrysdale/python-phonenumbers). This is a bummer, but there's hope.

