1527,IssuesEvent,2017-08-18 09:00:19+00:00,10155460,dbader/schedule,8612867,lawlietfans,,,opened,it works fine with scrapy module,[],[],0,"this module works fine with scrapy module, but do not using buitin `scrapy.cmdline`

```py
def crawl_work():
    cmdline.execute('scrapy crawl my_spider'.split())
if __name__=='__main__':
    schedule.every(1).minutes.do(crawl_work)
    while True:
            schedule.run_pending()
            time.sleep(1)
```
run only once, the program will exited.

change the scrapy.cmdline to subprocess
```py
def crawl_work():
    subprocess.Popen('scrapy crawl my_spider')
```
it works very well",{},{}
