3156,IssuesEvent,2016-09-19 07:52:22+00:00,6002572,santoshphilip/eppy,3817160,jamiebull1,,,closed,Work flow for contributors,[],[],7,"If you are a contributor, consider using the following workflow
- an issue is opened
- the issue is assigned to you
- You make a branch from `develop` with a meaningful name such as `i57_licence` where `i57` is the issue number
- Once the coding is complete and the tests pass, inform the ""release master""  of the repository.( release master   = @santoshphilip at present)
- ""release master"" will review and merge your changes into `develop`
- close the issue

If you are not a contributor
- ask to become a contributor

OR

- make a pull request
- make changes in the develop branch
- request a merge into the repository

(not sure I used the terminology correctly in the last few steps :-(",{},{}
