6538,IssuesEvent,2015-12-04 19:26:30+00:00,1643611,daviddrysdale/python-phonenumbers,8227371,jordanmnunez,,,opened,New Brazil mobile numbers are failing is_valid_number() method.,[],[],0,"Brazil mobile numbers are failing 

