6684,IssuesEvent,2016-10-15 19:58:06+00:00,20088879,serhatbolsu/robotframework-appiumlibrary,7917050,serhatbolsu,,,closed,Run a test on an existing session id,"[{'url': 'https://api.github.com/repos/serhatbolsu/robotframework-appiumlibrary/labels/question', 'name': 'question', 'color': 'cc317c'}]",[],2,"Hi,

