6777,IssuesEvent,2018-02-03 20:00:49+00:00,48501841,django/daphne,36182,andrewgodwin,27804,django,closed,Minor inconsistency in specification and implementation of http.request more_body key,[],[],1,"The specifications does not specify any default or requirement for the `more_body` key when sending [http.request type](https://github.com/django/asgiref/blob/master/specs/www.rst#request) but it is omitted in [Daphne](https://github.com/django/daphne/blob/db68c43de11014e68c1b79554f2dec2bbccb117a/daphne/http_protocol.py#L157-L158)

I assume it is optional and default False.",{},{}
