As far as I can see, the permissions are fine (at least for LaunchAgents) - but the file isn't there.

I should add I am not a watchman 'pro'. This is my first time working with it, and I'm stopped dead in my tracks. If I've overlooked something *obvious* let me know. Thanks for your time.
",{},{}
