7661,IssuesEvent,2017-07-25 18:04:26+00:00,2339473,bigcommerce/bigcommerce-api-python,27985126,sabotagebeats,186342,bigcommerce,closed,Unable to get ['meta']['pagination']['total_pages'] from products = api.Products.all() ,[],[],3,"### Expected behavior
in requests library, total_pages returned in json. 

