8610,IssuesEvent,2018-04-23 21:01:47+00:00,79510167,pypa/pipenv,270825,mvaled,647025,pypa,opened,Dependencies for locally installed distributions are not being taken into account,[],[],0,"Installing locally defined distributions doesn't properly process (and lock) their dependencies.  Steps to reproduce:

