9262,IssuesEvent,2018-05-14 10:54:29+00:00,32472033,peopledoc/django-chunkator,25185,brunobord,1080062,peopledoc,closed,Python 3.5 - PendingDeprecationWarning: generator 'chunkator_page' raised StopIteration,[],[],0,"Hello!
