9947,IssuesEvent,2015-02-24 15:27:45+00:00,3510804,GalSim-developers/GalSim,623887,rmjarvis,1462196,GalSim-developers,closed,Circular top-hat profile,[],[],2,"Hi - I would like to request a circular top-hat profile, or an ellipse more generally.

This would be useful to the Precision Projector Lab for modelling detector emulations in which the sources are simply illuminated holes.  The profile would always be convolved with a bandlimited PSF.  For now, we use PSFs much larger than the holes (approximate point sources), but this won't always be the case.

Thanks,
Chaz",{},{}
