10440,IssuesEvent,2017-12-30 21:23:49+00:00,35882519,zalando/connexion,488406,mohabusama,1564818,zalando,opened,Enable oauth token info verification using url params,[],[],0,"### Description

For OAUTH2 token verification, the token_info endpoint might support url params only. This is considered leaky and insecure [option](https://github.com/zalando/connexion/pull/542). However, since servers support this option, then it would be convenient to enable token verification using url params as a configuration during app initialization.

### Additional info:

E.g. https://developers.google.com/identity/sign-in/web/backend-auth
",{},{}
