10766,IssuesEvent,2018-08-13 21:44:16+00:00,81612762,trailofbits/manticore,2467355,mossberg,2314423,trailofbits,opened,Optimize event publishing,[],[],0,"Currently, no particular effort has been used to optimize the event publishing interface `Eventful._publish`. One common request is to make manticore faster, and this would be a key optimization point to look into. Events are published in many critical places within manticore, including tight loops, and the current implementation can be optimized in many ways to make the overhead of publishing events, especially events who have no registered handlers, faster.",{},{}
