PS C:\Users\Administrator\code\core> pex -o abc6.pex
PS C:\Users\Administrator\code\core> ls .\abc*


    Directory: C:\Users\Administrator\code\core


Mode                LastWriteTime         Length Name
----                -------------         ------ ----
-a----         4/8/2016   9:49 AM         286363 abc.pex
-a----         4/8/2016   9:52 AM         286298 abc4.pex
-a----         4/8/2016   9:52 AM         286310 abc5.pex
-a----         4/8/2016   9:54 AM         286364 abc6.pex
```

It looks like there are two separate issues.
+ Windows symlink support
+ Some confusion with the wheel package where pex expects an egg, but it looks like something else (a wheel?)

Confirming that both of these problems exist in master as of,

```
commit cfcfe708989b53ef790bd2733ed7a85cfd6e4e18
