11899,IssuesEvent,2018-05-29 04:30:36+00:00,49976939,learningequality/kolibri,2367265,indirectlylit,3926525,learningequality,closed,Content marked as visible to coaches is still visible to learners. ,[],[],1,"### Observed behavior
The lessons in this screenshot should only be visible to coaches and administrators:

![coach_only_lessons](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/15672948/40306931-d6f4e106-5d00-11e8-9f59-42e27fb81149.png)

They are still visible and accessible when logged in as a learner:

![viewing_lessons_as_learner](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/15672948/40307009-25e6835a-5d01-11e8-8c87-5931d23acafb.png)


### Expected behaviour
Learners should not be able to view content marked as visible to coaches. 

### User-facing consequences
Resources which are only meant to be viewed by coaches or administrators are visible to everyone.

### Steps to reproduce

1. Add some content in the Kolibri content studio
2. Mark content as visible to coaches
![set_visible_to_coaches](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/15672948/40307157-a1e462b0-5d01-11e8-8d6e-429fa5355021.png)
3. Publish content
