12565,IssuesEvent,2016-05-11 13:40:45+00:00,44518409,frictionlessdata/datapackage-py,297583,sirex,5912125,frictionlessdata,opened,push_datapackage does not support url as location specifier,[],[],0,"```python
import sqlalchemy as sa
