12697,IssuesEvent,2016-02-25 07:32:01+00:00,11589713,deis/deis,3526404,Joshua-Anderson,6117407,deis,reopened,feat(client) support pipes with deis config:push and deis:config pull,"[{'url': 'https://api.github.com/repos/deis/deis/labels/client', 'name': 'client', 'color': 'ff69b4'}, {'url': 'https://api.github.com/repos/deis/deis/labels/enhancement', 'name': 'enhancement', 'color': '84b6eb'}]",[],4,"It would be nice if deis config:push and deis:config pull supported piping like this:

