13768,IssuesEvent,2015-09-11 13:47:27+00:00,33653601,jupyter/notebook,151929,minrk,7388996,jupyter,closed,locating instructions for installing could be clearer,[],[],4,"So I scrolled up and down on the jupyter home page looking for an install button or link or something - its absence seemed sort of odd. Poking about I find the README in the notebook repo which is great but sorta terse (though to be honest worked great on OSX) and also found this link:

