14433,IssuesEvent,2016-05-23 16:06:10+00:00,45062555,F5Networks/f5-common-python,5366758,mac-reid,8935905,F5Networks,opened,Allow File and SSL Resource Naming,[],[],0,"First off, thanks for creating this! It really helps out.

