14468,IssuesEvent,2015-05-12 08:59:26+00:00,1151051,django-oscar/django-oscar,245297,mvantellingen,9057806,django-oscar,closed,Reverse for set_language not found,"[{'url': 'https://api.github.com/repos/django-oscar/django-oscar/labels/%E2%98%9B%20Needs%20more%20info', 'name': '☛ Needs more info', 'color': 'DDDDDD'}, {'url': 'https://api.github.com/repos/django-oscar/django-oscar/labels/%E2%9C%8E%20Docs', 'name': '✎ Docs', 'color': '444444'}]",[],4,"New install of django-oscar 1.0.1 on Python 3.4.

