14633,IssuesEvent,2015-11-03 06:17:12+00:00,26516210,letsencrypt/letsencrypt,106176,kuba,9289019,letsencrypt,reopened,Implement latest ACME spec changes,"[{'url': 'https://api.github.com/repos/letsencrypt/letsencrypt/labels/acme', 'name': 'acme', 'color': '888888'}, {'url': 'https://api.github.com/repos/letsencrypt/letsencrypt/labels/apache', 'name': 'apache', 'color': 'fbca04'}, {'url': 'https://api.github.com/repos/letsencrypt/letsencrypt/labels/nginx', 'name': 'nginx', 'color': 'eb6420'}, {'url': 'https://api.github.com/repos/letsencrypt/letsencrypt/labels/spec-compliance', 'name': 'spec-compliance', 'color': 'eb6420'}]",[],2,"Soon to be pulled in https://github.com/letsencrypt/boulder/pull/774 implements the following ACME spec changes:
