14886,IssuesEvent,2018-08-24 15:42:10+00:00,42750248,watson-developer-cloud/python-sdk,13935994,ehdsouza,10017763,watson-developer-cloud,closed,Response time for speech to text is more around 6 to 7 second ,"[{'id': 262304348, 'node_id': 'MDU6TGFiZWwyNjIzMDQzNDg=', 'url': 'https://api.github.com/repos/watson-developer-cloud/python-sdk/labels/support', 'name': 'support', 'color': '0e8a16', 'default': False}]",[],3,"#### Expected behavior
      Respond time within 1 second
   How I can get within 1 second Watson STT Response for 5-second Recording from Microphone 

#### Actual behavior
      Response time around 6 to 7 second
#### Steps to reproduce the problem
  Run the same code in your pc it will take 6 to 7 second to recognize via Watson STT Service

#### Code snippet (Note: Do not paste your credentials)
```py
from __future__ import print_function
import pyaudio
import tempfile
from watson_developer_cloud import SpeechToTextV1
from watson_developer_cloud.websocket import RecognizeCallback
import os.path
import datetime
import time

t1 = 0
