15689,IssuesEvent,2017-04-06 22:48:57+00:00,37496521,nteract/nteract,335567,Carreau,12401040,nteract,opened,multiple invocation of completer can break completer,[],[],0,"- create new notebook
- click in first empty cell
- press Ctrl-space 5 times. No hurry you can wait for the result to be shown, or be a brute and ctrl-space a lot.

Result: Completer will not show at the fifth invocation and console have: 

```
Uncaught TimeoutError {name: ""TimeoutError"", stack: ""TimeoutError: Timeout has occurred
at new Time... ~ /dev/nteract/lib/vendor.js:7956:12)"", message: ""Timeout has occurred""}
AsyncScheduler.flush @ /~/dev/nteract/lib/vendor.js:20502
```

Which is 

```
    AsyncScheduler.prototype.flush = function (action) {
        var actions = this.actions;
        if (this.active) {
            actions.push(action);
            return;
        }
        var error;
        this.active = true;
        do {
            if (error = action.execute(action.state, action.delay)) {
                break;
            }
        } while (action = actions.shift()); // exhaust the scheduler queue
        this.active = false;
        if (error) {
            while (action = actions.shift()) {
                action.unsubscribe();
            }
            throw error; 
        }
````

Completer is now completely deactivated.",{},{}
