18221,IssuesEvent,2017-08-31 14:01:16+00:00,78880128,instagrambot/instabot,12039393,sudoguy,26087671,instagrambot,closed,"I need to make my own wrap using c# and xamarin forms. I got send comments, post Likes, etc... But at instagram website doesn´t have the endpoint for direct message. I saw that have a url https://api.instagram.com/api/v1/direct_v2/threads/broadcast/text/ to send, but with wich parameters ?  Thanks for help.",[],[],0,"## Please follow the guide below

- Issues submitted without this template format will be **ignored**.
- You will be asked some questions and requested to provide some information, please read them **carefully** and answer completely.
- Put an `x` into all the boxes [ ] relevant to your issue (like so [x]).
